  <article id="books">
    <sect1>
      <title>Recommended Books</title>
      
      <para>The <ulink url="https://developer.gnome.org/gtkmm-tutorial/stable">Programming with gtkmm 4</ulink>
        and <ulink url="https://developer.gnome.org/gtkmm-tutorial/3.24/">Programming with gtkmm 3</ulink>
        tutorials are available online along with the rest of our <ulink url="documentation.html">documentation</ulink>.</para>
      <para><ulink url="https://mesonbuild.com/">The Meson build system</ulink> is also described online.</para>
      <para>
   The gtkmm developers also find these books helpful:
  </para>
